<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>既然明白 你们才该给我深呼吸一下</b></font>

250
00:14:19,820 --> 00:14:22,320
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>我们还必须再赢到更多的星</b></font>

251
00:14:23,070 --> 00:14:24,150
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>既然赢了就继续前进</b></font>

252
00:14:24,570 --> 00:14:25,690
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>那不是当然的吗</b></font>

253
00:14:26,360 --> 00:14:28,400
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>但是...开司</b></font>

254
00:14:28,930 --> 00:14:31,280
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>那家伙下一次会出什么牌已经很难...</b></font>

255
00:14:31,660 --> 00:14:33,080
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>没关系 交给我吧</b></font>

256
00:14:33,540 --> 00:14:34,540
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>一定会赢的</b></font>

257
00:14:35,300 --> 00:14:41,210
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>哦哦 这群家伙是类似紧急避难而聚集起来的废物的集合</b></font>

258
00:14:41,780 --> 00:14:45,260
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>不走运的三人组吗</b></font>

259
00:14:45,980 --> 00:14:46,650
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>怎么样</b></font>

260
00:14:47,820 --> 00:14:50,430
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>好吧 我就接受了</b></font>

261
00:14:50,750 --> 00:14:51,390
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>好</b></font>

262
00:14:53,810 --> 00:14:55,970
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>看不清局势的嚣张家伙</b></font>

263
00:14:56,810 --> 00:14:58,850
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>你们怎么可能会二连胜</b></font>

264
00:15:00,230 --> 00:15:01,520
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>看我踩碎你们</b></font>

265
00:15:04,130 --> 00:15:04,800
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>验牌</b></font>

266
00:15:05,470 --> 00:15:10,070
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>为什么啊 还以为是个会冷静考虑才比赛的人</b></font>

267
00:15:10,510 --> 00:15:11,110
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>放牌</b></font>

268
00:15:12,950 --> 00:15:16,330
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>不过确实 如果慢慢以理取胜的话</b></font>

269
00:15:16,490 --> 00:15:18,790
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>在规定时间能凑齐九颗星是不可能的</b></font>

270
00:15:19,330 --> 00:15:21,420
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>开司察觉到了这一点</b></font>

271
00:15:22,050 --> 00:15:25,460
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>不乘胜追击 向奇迹的连胜发起挑战的话</b></font>

272
00:15:25,670 --> 00:15:27,300
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>我们不可能活下来</b></font>

273
00:15:28,670 --> 00:15:29,260
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>开牌</b></font>

274
00:15:30,720 --> 00:15:32,930
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>拜托了 再出一次布...</b></font>

275
00:15:39,200 --> 00:15:39,830
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>可恶</b></font>

276
00:15:40,740 --> 00:15:43,510
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>傻瓜 这不是当然的吗</b></font>

277
00:15:44,020 --> 00:15:47,230
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>难道以为连出两次同一张牌还能赢吗</b></font>

278
00:15:48,180 --> 00:15:51,150
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>嗯 等等...也就是说</b></font>

279
00:15:51,810 --> 00:15:53,150
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>开司 我们走</b></font>

280
00:15:53,480 --> 00:15:54,050
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>嗯</b></font>

281
00:15:54,530 --> 00:15:58,040
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>喂 再来一次</b></font>

282
00:15:58,190 --> 00:15:58,750
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>哎?</b></font>

283
00:15:59,320 --> 00:16:01,670
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>刚才我答应了你的要求</b></font>

284
00:16:02,190 --> 00:16:05,130
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>这次该轮到你答应我了</b></font>

285
00:16:05,690 --> 00:16:07,260
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>开司 我们走吧</b></font>

286
00:16:07,600 --> 00:16:09,300
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>不用理他</b></font>

287
00:16:09,530 --> 00:16:10,070
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>嗯</b></font>

288
00:16:10,510 --> 00:16:12,470
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>所以你们才是废物</b></font>

289
00:16:13,720 --> 00:16:16,680
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>一个人什么都决定不了 垃圾</b></font>

290
00:16:18,770 --> 00:16:20,230
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>那是挑衅 挑衅</b></font>

291
00:16:20,520 --> 00:16:22,440
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>很明显的挑衅</b></font>

292
00:16:23,510 --> 00:16:25,310
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>来啊 开司</b></font>

293
00:16:25,900 --> 00:16:28,860
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>即使灰心丧气的坐着 星数也不会增加</b></font>

294
00:16:29,420 --> 00:16:31,350
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>好了 我们走吧 开司</b></font>

295
00:16:32,550 --> 00:16:34,620
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>不 不能退让</b></font>

296
00:16:35,760 --> 00:16:38,830
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>正如他所说 退让了星数也不会增加</b></font>

297
00:16:38,960 --> 00:16:40,060
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>你在说什么呢</b></font>

298
00:16:40,200 --> 00:16:41,630
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>你只有一颗星了</b></font>

299
00:16:41,730 --> 00:16:44,330
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>住手吧 开司 饶了我们吧</b></font>

300
00:16:46,030 --> 00:16:48,540
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>傻瓜 为什么不明白我在演戏</b></font>

301
00:16:48,540 --> 00:16:49,200
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>演戏?</b></font>

302
00:16:49,570 --> 00:16:51,140
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>第二战输给他是在我计算之中</b></font>

303
00:16:51,270 --> 00:16:52,070
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>是我撒的诱饵</b></font>

304
00:16:52,570 --> 00:16:54,510
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>现在鱼儿已经上钩了</b></font>

305
00:16:54,910 --> 00:16:56,850
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>放心吧 接下来就是二连胜</b></font>

306
00:17:02,920 --> 00:17:06,450
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>他说二连胜 哪有那种胜算</b></font>

307
00:17:06,820 --> 00:17:11,900
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>既然我们只有剪子 就是说对方会连出两次布了</b></font>

308
00:17:12,320 --> 00:17:14,280
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>那怎么可能</b></font>

309
00:17:14,570 --> 00:17:16,360
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>开司一定是确信了吧</b></font>

310
00:17:17,410 --> 00:17:19,780
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>的确 注重平衡的鬣狗</b></font>

311
00:17:20,140 --> 00:17:23,120
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>很难想像他接下来会连出两张布</b></font>

312
00:17:24,010 --> 00:17:28,670
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>如果他出的话 那一定是他确信开司会出石头</b></font>

313
00:17:29,130 --> 00:17:32,960
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>或是他认为只要出布就可立于不败之地</b></font>

314
00:17:33,450 --> 00:17:34,470
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>也就是说</b></font>

315
00:17:36,420 --> 00:17:37,320
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>古畑</b></font>

316
00:17:38,290 --> 00:17:40,820
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>安藤 开司会赢的</b></font>

317
00:17:42,470 --> 00:17:44,690
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>他会连续出两次布</b></font>

318
00:17:45,130 --> 00:17:46,560
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>为什么会这样?</b></font>

319
00:17:47,100 --> 00:17:48,900
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>他的平衡理论啊</b></font>

320
00:17:49,230 --> 00:17:51,370
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>在接下来的第三战就会复苏了</b></font>

321
00:17:51,700 --> 00:17:53,100
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>他的平衡理论</b></font>

322
00:17:53,740 --> 00:17:56,670
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>所以他才执着的再次要求开司比赛</b></font>

323
00:17:56,940 --> 00:17:59,320
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>平衡理论复苏?</b></font>

324
00:18:00,110 --> 00:18:02,440
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>连续出了两次剪子的开司</b></font>

325
00:18:02,710 --> 00:18:07,380
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>剩下的两张卡还都是剪子 你觉得他会这样想吗</b></font>

326
00:18:08,620 --> 00:18:13,050
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>他在第一战时 应该就认定开司的卡是两张剪子</b></font>

327
00:18:13,520 --> 00:18:16,830
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>以及石头和布各一张</b></font>

328
00:18:17,680 --> 00:18:20,260
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>那样的话 现在开司所剩下的卡</b></font>

329
00:18:20,550 --> 00:18:22,140
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>就是石头和布各一张</b></font>

330
00:18:22,390 --> 00:18:24,930
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>或者某一方有两张</b></font>

331
00:18:25,680 --> 00:18:29,560
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>也就是说 第三战开始只要出布就能赢</b></font>

332
00:18:30,210 --> 00:18:31,440
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>最坏的情况也是平局</b></font>

333
00:18:31,940 --> 00:18:33,640
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>他确信不可能会输</b></font>

334
00:18:33,940 --> 00:18:34,980
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>是吗</b></font>

335
00:18:35,610 --> 00:18:39,780
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>开司就在等他出现这样的思考 所以去和他比赛了</b></font>

336
00:18:41,120 --> 00:18:41,820
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>验牌</b></font>

337
00:18:42,380 --> 00:18:44,150
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>没错 开司在等待</b></font>

338
00:18:45,520 --> 00:18:50,540
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>等待敌人自己踏入泥沼 低着头等待着</b></font>

339
00:18:50,960 --> 00:18:51,540
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>放牌</b></font>

340
00:18:52,340 --> 00:18:54,090
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>去死吧 垃圾</b></font>

341
00:18:54,590 --> 00:18:57,170
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>这等待正是开司的妙技</b></font>

342
00:18:58,090 --> 00:19:01,400
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>下地狱去吧 开牌</b></font>

343
00:19:09,940 --> 00:19:12,860
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>怎...怎么可能 为什么</b></font>

344
00:19:14,980 --> 00:19:15,650
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>那么再见了</b></font>

345
00:19:16,420 --> 00:19:17,190
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>等一等</b></font>

346
00:19:17,850 --> 00:19:21,280
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>再比一场 没错 给我回来 开司</b></font>

347
00:19:28,430 --> 00:19:29,230
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>古畑</b></font>

348
00:19:31,430 --> 00:19:34,000
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>潜伏在平衡理论中的泥沼</b></font>

349
00:19:34,500 --> 00:19:37,590
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>一旦踏入就无法轻易从中逃脱</b></font>

350
00:19:38,870 --> 00:19:41,780
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>因为 平衡支配了思考</b></font>

351
00:19:42,340 --> 00:19:44,880
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>这一世界观 理论 常识中</b></font>

352
00:19:45,150 --> 00:19:47,980
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>是不存在手牌全部是剪子的状况的</b></font>

353
00:19:48,770 --> 00:19:50,480
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>这种情况根本难以想像</b></font>

354
00:19:51,060 --> 00:19:51,730
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>验牌</b></font>

355
00:19:52,520 --> 00:19:54,020
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>他不可能再出剪子了</b></font>

356
00:19:55,020 --> 00:19:55,650
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>放牌</b></font>

357
00:19:56,070 --> 00:19:58,650
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>四张都是剪子 那是绝对不可能的</b></font>

358
00:19:59,190 --> 00:20:00,200
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>开牌</b></font>

359
00:20:06,570 --> 00:20:10,410
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>因为连续三次都来了同样的牌 所以不可能再来同样的牌了</b></font>

360
00:20:11,160 --> 00:20:14,170
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>在赌博中 这种想法是最为危险的</b></font>

361
00:20:14,980 --> 00:20:16,880
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>不可能是剪子 不可能是...</b></font>

362
00:20:23,820 --> 00:20:26,600
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>深陷其中 无法逃脱的通向崩坏之路</b></font>

363
00:20:27,490 --> 00:20:29,820
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>名为赌博的魔性正在一旁讥笑</b></font>

364
00:20:30,960 --> 00:20:34,330
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>为什么 为什么会有四张</b></font>

365
00:20:35,600 --> 00:20:36,460
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>偶然罢了</b></font>

366
00:20:36,980 --> 00:20:39,110
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>偶然? 你说偶然</b></font>

367
00:20:42,040 --> 00:20:45,770
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>也就是说 你的推测 理论并没有错</b></font>

368
00:20:47,010 --> 00:20:49,840
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>但只要走错一步 那就是盲点</b></font>

369
00:20:50,580 --> 00:20:53,460
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>人类一旦相信某个理论是正确的</b></font>

370
00:20:53,580 --> 00:20:55,000
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>就很难再去怀疑它</b></font>

371
00:20:56,380 --> 00:21:00,550
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>更何况是靠那理论赢到现在的家伙 就更是如此了</b></font>

372
00:21:01,390 --> 00:21:03,160
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>因为有理论在所以毫无防备</b></font>

373
00:21:03,830 --> 00:21:06,690
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>开司 反过来利用了理论而获得的二连胜</b></font>

